<!--
  This lists your main pages so Google knows they exist. Individual
  blog posts aren't auto-added here (this is a plain file, not a
  database) — when you add a real blog post in src/data/blogPosts.ts,
  also add a <url> entry for it below, following the pattern under
  "blog posts" near the bottom. It's optional (Google can still find
  posts by following links from your Blog page) but it helps.
-->
